---
const videoUrl = "/videos/vide.mp4"; 
---

<section class="video-showcase">
  <div class="video-wrapper">
    
    <video 
      autoplay 
      muted 
      loop 
      playsinline 
      class="bg-video"
      poster="/images/poster-video.jpg" 
    >
      <source src={videoUrl} type="video/mp4" />
      Tu navegador no soporta videos acaso usas Internet Explorer? jajajajaa.
    </video>

    <div class="video-overlay"></div>

    <div class="video-content">
      <span class="video-tag">Excelencia en Acero</span>
      <h2 class="video-title">Precisi√≥n que Brilla</h2>
      <div class="decorative-line"></div>
      <p class="video-description">
        Cada soldadura y acabado es tratado como una pieza de arte industrial.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .video-showcase {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 70vh; 
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 60px 0;
    background-color: #000;
  }

  .video-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .bg-video {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    min-width: 100%;
    min-height: 100%;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }


  .video-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg, 
      rgba(164, 20, 44, 0.4) 0%, 
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6) 100%
    );
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .video-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 20px;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .video-tag {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #caa9a8; 
  }

  .video-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; 
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .decorative-line {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 auto 30px;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .video-description {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 200;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

 
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .video-showcase {
      height: 50vh;
    }
    .video-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>